{"tid":577402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲官員說中國避孕套太細 網民：辱華，斷交！","createTime":"2018-03-01T17:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T18:29:19.000Z","uid":129148,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7d8b67ddb0ebe54c3b344640fb733810c188e5","tid":577402,"uid":129148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"非洲官員說中國避孕套太細 網民：辱華，斷交！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180301/large/1519900019_b47a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180301%2Flarge%2F1519900019_b47a.jpg&h=1c2421f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強國網民的心，真的這麼硊弱？津巴布韋衛生部長David Parirenyatwa稱，當地愛滋病、性病問題嚴峻，使用安全套是最有效的方法，可是，他表示大部份由中國進口的安全套「尺碼太細」，完全不合用。有強國的網民稱這番言論是「辱華」、「挑釁」，網上大罵，更稱要「強烈譴責」，甚至「必須斷交」。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Parirenyatwa日前公佈當地計劃成立對抗愛滋病、性病的新項目，他表示去年當地安全套銷量達1億個，平均每名男性購買33個，可是，他卻稱<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目前當地的安全套大部份都是由中國進口，不少男性都投訴這些安全套太小，不合用</span></span>。他更向內地的企業自行製造年輕人喜愛的安全套，稱應是一筆大生意。<br />\n這則報道傳到內地，即時引發網民起哄：「津巴布韋辱華！」不少網民都說冿巴布韋的言論，是「國家級人身攻擊」，「有損我大國形象」，「這種的行為必須強烈譴責」，甚至有網民稱「這種國家必須斷交」。可是，有網民卻稱內地的民眾都不愛用國貨，那有資格罵別人：「中國市場的高級安全套基本都是日本、美國、泰國生產的！」<br />\n觀察者網  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑你細JJ啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b78067e52f2674e979d5e423f457c49e5a981e","tid":577402,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T17:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37bee9df07b64c2f54486974cabb68a6064b5ca","tid":577402,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T17:30:30.000Z","msg":"中國市場的高級安全套基本都是日本、美國、泰國生產的<br />\n咁仲衰 啫係全世界都知你地細J<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2670cf2029aba7894ece6cc1ebcebc8551390c","tid":577402,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T17:32:45.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca7ca726d8de36ff7b080c103a5a1bf67828f10","tid":577402,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T18:25:03.000Z","msg":"中國有啲套真係零彈性<br />\n52就真係52<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5785707070cf9453bce94f84c88660ea034e5b","tid":577402,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T18:29:19.000Z","msg":"好似之前有個表，香港人比支那長少少，比日韓都長啲，以亞洲同樣人種嚟講算霸主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過黑人全球最長的確又係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}